title: How to Succeed
author: Dimterion
description: An everlasting story of achieving greatness.

d5cd557f-04e9-46cf-b382-269c51de118d.label: Node 1
d5cd557f-04e9-46cf-b382-269c51de118d.text: You wake up in the morning with the idea of a story.

8e483f0b-4ff5-438c-8edd-43bf293fba96.label: Node 2
8e483f0b-4ff5-438c-8edd-43bf293fba96.text: You continue your day as usual, nothing happens.

2cc8dfed-5efd-452a-89be-c94a73e63f8f.label: Node 3
2cc8dfed-5efd-452a-89be-c94a73e63f8f.text: You develop the idea and create something great.

options.text: Give up and go back to your routine

4eaedd7d-7107-4e92-b48b-c89e6564cd90.label: Node 4
4eaedd7d-7107-4e92-b48b-c89e6564cd90.text: Now you have more ideas in mind.

options.text: Start working on all of your ideas at once
Focus on your initial idea and develop it fully

b25df5d9-b2c3-49cb-a275-dce876692990.label: Node 5
b25df5d9-b2c3-49cb-a275-dce876692990.text: You get overwhelmed and want to go back to sleep.

125585e4-7b33-40a4-88b7-34053193a491.label: Node 6
125585e4-7b33-40a4-88b7-34053193a491.text: You achieve success and can now develop other ideas.
